b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2282,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Announcing Gala Dragalia!","message":"<div>Gala Dragalia will start at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1625032800\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?<\/div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5\\u2605 summon or 5\\u2605 featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">Note: The newly added 5\\u2605 adventurer Summer Alex (flame) will also appear in the next summon showcase.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Newly added featured adventurer and dragon:<\/div><div>\\u25a0Adventurer<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Summer Alex (flame\/bow)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Dragon<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Reborn Nidhogg (shadow)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1625032800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1625464799\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured adventurer and dragon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured dragon:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/ec5f14fa15dcc24d95a53ff2c4f69469.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>368<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>128<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,296<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>Nidhogg, wicked wyrm with dominion over death<br>itself, reborn into a new form. Freed from wicked<br>miasma by a maiden\'s determination, he takes a<br>newfound interest in humanity\\u2014not just in their<br>ends, as before, but now in their lives as well.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1dc2f6f0f6e043a02de111856f4d5c092.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Doomsday Eclipse<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to the target and nearby enemies.<br>Enemies in break state take reduced damage.<br>If the user is targeting an enemy and not using a<br>skill when their remaining shapeshift time runs out,<br>this skill will be used automatically, regardless of<br>whether or not the skill gauge is filled.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 300 \\u00d7 8 hits<br>Damage Modifier:<br>\\u30fb75% against enemies in break state<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Shadow) Strength +70%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Shadow: <br>increases strength by 70%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/cc742aec48d0c0c0acbec0b24732a2662.png\\"><\/span><span>(Shadow) Throes of Eternity II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Shadow:<br>adds 30% to the modifier applied to damage<br>against light-attuned enemies and enemies<br>with no attunement for 45 seconds every time<br>the dragon gauge fills by 10%. This increase<br>will not stack, and, after activating, this ability<br>will not activate again for five seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured adventurer:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/0198b1991018428318e76ce8844eebf4.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9aad909ba3c17275f9fd58ab5d60b7522.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>803<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>471<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>2,514<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Adventurer Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>Attired in airy aquatic apparel, Alex sets out for<br>her first-ever vacation alongside her dear friend<br>Elisanne. The sun shines at last on this girl once<br>veiled in darkness, lighting the way for her to<br>make irreplaceable summer memories.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/43a91d6c3c412fe83430cfe1fa61a5722.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Tropical Snipe<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>7<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies in a line,<br>and lowers their scorchrend resistance.<br><br>If this skill is used directly after Burning Bonds,<br>the following variant of this skill will be used instead:<br>deals damage to enemies in a line, lowers their<br>scorchrend resistance, and removes Scorchbloom<br>from enemies hit by this attack. The removal of<br>Scorchbloom will not count as a buff having been<br>dispelled.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,626 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,560<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbScorchrend Res -20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:<\/color><br>Damage: 2,355 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,560<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 18,430<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbScorchrend Res -20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/0a5f27e3a882a180f519fc89863948262.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Burning Bonds<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Grants the user a strength amp, deals damage<br>to enemies in a line, and applies \\"Scorchbloom\\"<br>to them.<br><br>When Scorchbloom is lost, the affected enemy<br>will take damage and be inflicted with scorchrend.<br>Scorchbloom is lost when its remaining time is<br>depleted or when removed with the Tropical Snipe<br>skill, but it cannot be removed by attacks or effects<br>that dispel buffs.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 2,065 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,140<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbScorchbloom<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u3000\\u3000Cannot be reapplied while active<br>Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 3)<br><br><color=#00008B>When Scorchbloom is Lost:<\/color><br>Damage: 1,432 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbScorchrend<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 41.6<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Skill Haste +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases skill gauge fill rate by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9313ae9aa920e91dfb0863136ae5dc042.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Flame) Combo Time VI<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Flame:<br>extends the window between them hitting an enemy<br>and the combo counter resetting by 2.5 seconds.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/71d793fb535ac808bdfe31e27ebe9b8b2.png\\"><\/span><span>Flurry Scorchrend Edge & Sting II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When the combo count is 15 or higher,<br>increases the chances of inflicting scorchrend<br>by 50% and its duration by 30%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1a55c9cd31df1c438cd55d10b0a536742.png\\"><\/span><span>Sleep Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to sleep by 100%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/71d793fb535ac808bdfe31e27ebe9b8b2.png\\"><\/span><span>Strength Amp = Scorchrend Edge & Sting II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When the user has a strength amp,<br>increases the chances of inflicting scorchrend<br>by 30% and its duration by 30%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div>\\u30fbAdventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<\/div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for adventurers featured in this summon showcase will go on sale, and it will cost fewer items to unlock their skins. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1624946400,"prev_article_id":"2288","next_article_id":"2318","image_path":"","update_time":1624930607}}}'